title: Letter to Jerry
author: walrusmanatee68
pages:
#- Dear Jerry,
    I will announce to you buisiness ideas for Walrus Corp.  from my new home via skype.  Once I am settled again, and PLEYAA builds the marketplace in Elysia your job will be to maintain stores there, the private office (my old home), and the
#- public office (castle).  Your payments will be 75% of all income from the Elysia stores, which will be recorded by a Google Doc. that I will design.  Once Elysia is public you are free to hire employees for your region from surrounding cities and Elysia. 
#- You may sell anything at the store you deem fit, and things required by myself.  For current funds you may use a diamond vein at the coordinates x: -7426 y: 71 z: 5627, this vein is approximately 740m from the private Walrus Corp. office.
#- For further information regarding the business contact me.

Sincerely,
walrusmanatee68
/u/bestwalrus68
